 Educational Background



 


Columbia University

                  Columbia University is one of the world's most important centers of research and at the same time a distinctive and distinguished learning environment for undergraduates and graduate students in many scholarly and professional fields. The University recognizes the importance of its location in New York City and seeks to link its research and teaching to the vast resources of a great metropolis. It seeks to attract a diverse and international faculty and student body, to support research and teaching on global issues, and to create academic relationships with many countries and regions. It expects all areas of the university to advance knowledge and learning at the highest level and to convey the products of its efforts to the world.                





 Career History



Chairman, President & Chief Executive Officer

                                    2007 - Current                


Advent Claymore Convertible Securities & Income Fund II


                  Advent Claymore Convertible Securities & Income Fund II is a closed end investment trust. It focuses on convertible securities and non-convertible income-producing securities, each of U.S. and non-U.S. issuers. The fund was founded on May 24, 2007 and is headquartered in New York, NY.                




Founder, President & Chief Investment Officer

                                    2001 - Current                


Advent Capital Management LLC


                  Advent specializes in convertible, high yield and equity strategies.  The firm manages over $6 billion in long-only products, hedge funds and closed-end mutual funds - providing a broad view of the market and the ability to take advantage of opportunities across the entire capital structure, globally. Our structure enables us to fully understand and implement various investment strategies including stocks, bonds, convertibles, credit default swaps, options and other derivatives.

Advent manages three synergistic lines of business which includes long-only strategies, hedge fund strategies and closed-end mutual funds which are listed on the NYSE.  Since inception, our credit-driven research focus has been a core driver of our investment success in both long-only and hedged strategies. Our success can be measured by the consistent performance we have achieved across the firm’s products.

We add value by performing thorough internal credit research that translates into consistent returns with low volatility by protecting against the downside. We utilize a dynamic bottom-up, relative value approach to security selection. Our proprietary credit driven research process is designed to identify the most attractive securities with stable-to-improving fundamentals which offer upside potential and downside protection.

Our global infrastructure is supported by a team of highly talented investment professionals with deep experience across the entire capital structure in global convertible, equity, high yield and bank loan markets. With offices in New York and London we are able to trade seamlessly around the clock.                




Fund Advisor

                                    Current                


Guggenheim Funds Investment Advisors LLC


                  Guggenheim Funds Investment Advisors offers a variety of strategic investment solutions including innovative investment strategies employing the use of ETFs, unit investment trusts (UITs) and closed-end funds.                




President & Chief Executive Officer

                                    Prior - 2012                


Advent Claymore Global Convertible Securities & Income Fund


                  Advent Claymore Global Convertible Securities & Income Fund. is a Closed-End Investment Fund/Investment Trust. The company is headquartered in New York, NY.                




Director, Capital Markets Division-Convertible Securities Department

                                    Prior                


Merrill Lynch & Co.


                  Merrill Lynch is one of the world’s premier providers of wealth management, securities trading and sales, corporate finance and investment banking services.                





