Bloomberg Markets Hedge Fund & Investor Summit

                  Bloomberg Markets Hedge Fund & Investor Summit: The World's Leading Hedge Fund Managers & Investors Discuss Opportunity Beyond the Crisis is the first annual, invitation-only gathering of the world’s smartest minds in the hedge fund and institutional investing industries. Throughout the more than 20 interviews, panel discussions and debates, we’ll explore the latest economic and financial trends dictating global markets as they start to emerge from the worst downturn since the Great Depression, and provide insight for investors to understand where their money can best perform.
Featured speakers, including managers who made the Bloomberg Markets magazine Richest Hedge Funds ranking in 2010, have profited from investing in a broad range of fields such as distressed securities, convertible bonds and emerging markets. Institutional investors include managers of public and private pension funds, university and foundation endowments and sovereign wealth funds.
The more than 100 executives in attendance will include portfolio managers from top performing and mid-sized hedge funds, chief investment officers from sovereign wealth funds, pension funds, and major university endowments, c-suite banking officials, economists and lawmakers.                





